snippet.title: PS2 Longplay [001] Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater (part 1 of 9)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.net

Played By: RickyC

Replacement for other mgs3 longplay. Better video quality + less shot gun frenzy mode. Youtube is having some problems with upload so other parts will come out whenever they can.

The cave area in the video is darker than it should be and is how I saw it on my tv which fixes darkness at that level for everything. The darkness is only for a short while though and gives it more atmosphere. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
